<paragraph blockId="22.[160,1156,809,904]" box="[160,409,809,835]" pageId="22" pageNumber="287">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,409,809,835]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="287">External morphology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[160,1156,809,904]" pageId="22" pageNumber="287">Body elongate, narrow, background colour black. Rhinophores smooth; oral veil very well developed and without oral tentacles. Cerata lateral, elongated; tip swollen.</paragraph>
